data.title: Maritime Mosaic
data.text:
Lawrence MacPherson

M, #974, b. circa 1940, d. 19 May 2011

Father: Daniel Thomas MacPherson1 b. 21 Oct 1907, d. 28 Jul 1996

Mother: Mary Jessie Cameron2 b. 2 Dec 1906, d. 17 Jun 1986

Relationships: 4th great-grandson of Dougald MacFarlane, 4th great-grandson of Margaret MacDonell, 1st cousin of Donald James MacFarlane

Charts: Descendants of Ewan Cameron & Margaret Gillis, Descendants of Hugh Gillis & (?) MacEachern, Descendants of Donald Gillis & Catherine MacGillivray, Descendants of Alexander Beaton & Ann MacBain, Descendants of Angus Walker & Catherine MacDougall

The ancestry chart of Archibald MacFarlane (ID # 34) is presented because he unites the ancestry of both his parents. If an individual appears more than once in Archibald's chart this indicates descent from the individual in more than one line. By clicking on the each instance (i.e. Ancestry of Archibald MacFarlane (#5)) each line of descent will be shown.
